Title: Vortex Line Nucleation of First-Order Transition U(1)-Symmetric Field

SystemsComments: Author Information under

paper also atJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B460 (1999) 36-40

We show that in field systems with U(1)-symmetry, first-order transitions arenucleated by vortex lines, not bubbles, thus calling for a reinvestigation ofthe Kibble mechanism for the phase transition of the early universe.